<item>
            <title>[LU-1479] SRP module enabled by lbuild</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1479</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;currently, srp initiator and target modules are disabled by lbuild when it builds kernel-ib RPM.&lt;br/&gt;
What&apos;s reason of disabling this module? We don&apos;t need SRP target module, but want to include SRP initiator module in kernel-ib.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
